  "profile": {
    "summary": "Zainab Okonkwo is a 25-year-old Nigerian fashion designer and creative director based in Lagos. She is the founder of 'Zuri Lagos', a brand specializing in fusion Afro-contemporary womenswear that balances modesty with expressive style. A self-taught digital pattern-maker, Zainab's work has gained significant traction, evidenced by her 280k Instagram followers and features in publications like Vogue Africa. She is passionate about mentoring young seamstresses and aims to showcase her designs at New York Fashion Week.",
